name: Innocence In The Cage
description:
It's a digital piece by Mrs M.Heydari as a member of Sepas art group.

I am an Afghan woman and I want freedom!
There is shame in my nature.
I know where I should be ashamed
And where should I be free.
They have plucked the wings and feathers of my dreams and imprisoned me in the prison of ignorance.

It's for Afghan girls, wishing them freedom.
